{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-js","path":"/docs/update.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>Some changes are not backwards-compatible, if you update to the latest version and you have customisations depending on an old version, they might stop working properly. Fixing this usually does not take a lot of time, nevertheless bear that in mind when updating.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"getting-the-latest-minor-release\"><a href=\"#getting-the-latest-minor-release\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Getting the latest minor release</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Update the theme in <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">vendor</code></li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"39096752422300795000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# Update the theme and all of its dependencies\ncomposer update scandipwa/*`, `39096752422300795000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Update the theme and all of its dependencies</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">composer</span> update scandipwa/*</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>If the release note says something has been changed in the configuration, manually update the <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">src/config</code> folder in your customisations folder (default <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">app/design/frontend/.....</code>), merging in all the changes from the new version. This process does not happen automatically. Be careful when doing that, the project may not work at all or work incorrectly with broken configuration. If the project does not work after an upgrade, outdated <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">config</code> folder is often the cause.</li>\n<li>Read the release note and determine whether some other action is required in terms of refactoring your code corresponding to the new functionality. This will be the case for ScandiPWA v3 and its new plugin mechanism.</li>\n<li>Fix all the non backwards compatible changes breaking your project by reviewing your modifications on top of them.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"getting-the-latest-major-release\"><a href=\"#getting-the-latest-major-release\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Getting the latest major release</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Update the <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">scandipwa/installer</code> dependency in your <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">src/composer.json</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>Remember about the <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">minimum-stability</code> setting, if you wish to install a pre-release version.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Launch the project and run the following command</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"16086181024896895000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`composer install`, `16086181024896895000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">composer</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Go through all the steps of updating to the latest minor except the first one.</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"Theme Upgrade to the latest version"},"fields":{"path":"content/docs/update.md","slug":"/docs/update.html"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/docs/update.html"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}